After becoming popular, it was immediately confiscated by the local government as an illegal building
Recently, there was news that the local government would not demolish the illegal building, but would preserve the landscape and develop it into a tourist attraction
As soon as the news came out, the comment area was in an uproar, and some people said that their own store was also destroyed in this way
